%puruṣasya nityadarśanāt gītaśravaṇāt  vallabhavastuno  darśanāt  yaḥ ānanda utpadyate     svargalokaḥ               kathyate  rogapīḍano durjanebhya  puruṣasya yad duḥkhaṃ utpadyate// tadbahutaraṃ  narakaṃ kathyate// \L
