%puruṣasyāvādya   nṛtyodgītaśravaṇād  vallabhavasttuno  darśanād  yā  ānanda utpadyate sa bahurānaṃdaḥ svargaphalaḥ? kathyate  rogapīḍa   durjanebhyaḥ puruṣasya duḥkham     utpadyate       bahutaraṃ narakaṃ kathyate \U1
