 \note[type=source, labelb=314, nosep]{ \approx  SSP 6.10 (Ed. p. 111): yasya dhairyamayo daṇḍaḥ parākāśaṃ ca kharparaṃ | yogapaṭṭaṃ nijāśaktiḥ so 'vadhūto 'bhidhīyate |}
